response.overview: Empress  Team member  In the heart of the Roman Empire, Villia, the rebellious daughter of a ruthless emperor, refuses to live a life of luxury while her people suffer. When she's denied the chance to train as a warrior because she's a woman, Villia takes fate into her own hands-cutting her hair, forging armor, and entering the brutal world of gladiators under a false identity and truth. But in the blood-soaked sands of the arena, secrets are hard to keep-and when enemies of the empire begin to uncover who she really is, Villia must fight not just for her survival, but for her legacy. What begins as a bold mission to prove herself becomes a war for the soul of Rome.
response.tagline: One woman can change rome forever.
response.title: Empress
